---
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';

const { user } = Astro.locals;
if (!user) return Astro.redirect('/login');
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <title>Acesso Pendente – Ygor Luan Academy</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />

    <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-20 text-center">
      <div class="mb-8" style="color: var(--copper); font-size: 3rem;">⏳</div>

      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: var(--cream);">
        Acesso pendente
      </h1>

      <p class="font-sans text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--fade); line-height: 1.75;">
        Sua conta existe, mas ainda não identificamos um pagamento aprovado vinculado a ela.
        Se você acabou de comprar, pode levar alguns minutos para o acesso ser liberado — tente novamente em instantes.
      </p>

      <p class="font-sans text-sm mb-10" style="color: var(--fade);">
        Se acredita que houve um erro, entre em contato pelo e-mail
        <a href="mailto:suporte@ygorluanacademy.com.br" style="color: var(--copper); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px;">
          suporte@ygorluanacademy.com.br
        </a>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/#comprar" class="btn-primary">
          Adquirir o curso
        </a>

        <form method="POST" action="/api/auth/signout">
          <button type="submit" class="btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto">
            Sair da conta
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
